Uganda Opposition Leader Besigye in Standoff With Police After Protest

-- B y   F r e d   O j a m b o
-- 
2011-04-14T07:58:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/uganda-opposition-leader-besigye-in-standoff-with-police-after-protest.html
Uganda main opposition leader Kizza
Besigye is in a standoff with police, who want to arrest him
after disrupting a walk he was leading to protest rising fuel
and food costs, police spokeswoman Judith Nabakooba said by
phone from Kampala today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Ojambo in Kampala at 
 fojambo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
